EXTREME WEATHER

EM-DAT: The Emergency Events Database - Université catholique de Louvain (UCL) - CRED, www.emdat.be, Brussels, Belgium. Classification: https://emdat.be/classification -> extreme_weather_raw.csv



GREENHOUSE GAS (GHG) EMISSIONS

https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/products-datasets/-/sdg_13_10 -> ghg_emissions_indexed_and_per_capita.tsv
https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/national-emissions-reported-to-the-unfccc-and-to-the-eu-greenhouse-gas-monitoring-mechanism-15 -> ghg_emissions_per_sector_raw.csv
https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/greenhouse-gas-emission-projections-for-4 -> ghg_emissions_projections_raw.csv




TEMPERATURE

https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/indicators/global-and-european-temperature-8/assessment -> temperature_deviations_raw.csv


SEA LEVEL
Digital Elevation Model Over Europe (EU-DEM), from the Copernicus project: https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/eu-dem#tab-metadata

RCP4.5 total sea level rise projections, from the Integrated Climate Data Center (ICDC): https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/external/ar5-sea-level-rise-projections

long term predictions: Winkelmann, R., Levermann, A., Ridgwell, A., & Caldeira, K. (2015). Combustion of available fossil-fuel resources sufficient to eliminate the Antarctic ice sheet, Sci. Adv., 1, e1500589.



EU | Population: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/products-datasets/-/namq_10_pe

EU | Population projections: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/products-datasets/-/tps00002

EU | Temperature deviations: https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/daviz/european-average-air-temperature-anomalies-8#tab-chart_8

EU | Greenhouse gas emissions per sector (National emissions reported to the UNFCCC and to the EU Greenhouse Gas Monitoring Mechanism): https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/national-emissions-reported-to-the-unfccc-and-to-the-eu-greenhouse-gas-monitoring-mechanism-15

EU | Greenhouse gas emissions indexed and per capita: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/products-datasets/-/sdg_13_10

EU | Greenhouse gas emissions projections: https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/greenhouse-gas-emission-projections-for-4

Not EU | Extreme weather: The Emergency Events Database - Université catholique de Louvain (UCL) - CRED, www.emdat.be, Brussels, Belgium. Classification: https://emdat.be/classification
